  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Interventional study of modulation of immune response in patients with pancreatic tubular
      adenocarcinoma after resection and gemcitabine treatment. When included, patients are
      pre-treated with moderate doses of cyclophosphamide. Then infusions of allogeneic mononuclear
      cells are given.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
