  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  ECOG performance status 0-2 at the time of inclusion

          -  Following R0 or R1 pancreatic tubular adenocarcinoma resection and adjuvant
             gemcitabine treatment

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Less than 3 mths expected survival

          -  Serious comorbidity

          -  Age above 70 yrs
      </textblock>
